ope\nEXISTS subqueries in createDescendantsSql() and createChildrenSql(), so the\nplanner can drive the scan from idx_event_ou_occurreddate before evaluating\ncorrelated scope checks.\n\nDESCENDANTS: ev.organisationunitid IN (SELECT organisationunitid FROM\norganisationunit WHERE path LIKE CONCAT(:ou_path, '%'))\n\nCHILDREN: (ev.organisationunitid = :ou_id OR ev.organisationunitid IN\n(SELECT organisationunitid FROM organisationunit WHERE parentid = :ou_id))\n\nThe path LIKE and hierarchylevel checks are retained inside the scope EXISTS\nsubqueries for ACL correctness. Semantics are unchanged.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e","author":{"name":"Jason Pickering","email":"jason@dhis2.org"},"id":"cdfb0fbbf8bb1b095241ee3fa9ffc41d7aa14782","tree_id":"4f4fddb7a0f2fb3d48f5df8cca7ae8de5146e7da","timestamp":"2026-04-16T09:11:37Z","committer":{"name":"Jason Pickering","email":"jason@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/5591308","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/subscriptions"},"na